ZH: 我指望你按时完成这个任务。
EN: I rely on you to complete this task on time.

ZH: 她指望这个职位能给她更好的薪水。
EN: She hopes that this position will give her a better salary.

ZH: 我们不能只指望运气，还要加倍努力。
EN: We can't just rely on luck, we also need to work harder.

ZH: 他指望他的朋友帮助他解决问题。
EN: He counts on his friends to help him solve problems.

ZH: 这些学生指望老师能提供更多的指导。
EN: These students expect the teacher to provide more guidance.

ZH: 我不指望别人的帮助，我可以自己完成。
EN: I don't count on others' help, I can do it myself.

ZH: 你不能一直指望父母的支持，要学会独立。
EN: You can't always rely on your parents' support, you need to learn to be independent.

ZH: 她指望这个机会能够实现她的梦想。
EN: She hopes that this opportunity can fulfill her dreams.

ZH: 我指望这个项目能够取得成功。
EN: I have high hopes for the success of this project.

ZH: 你可以指望我始终支持你。
EN: You can count on me for constant support.

