EN: She hopes that her efforts will be recognized.

ZH: 他指望这笔投资能够带来巨大的回报。
EN: He expects this investment to bring huge returns.

ZH: 我们指望这个会议能够解决争议。
EN: We hope that this meeting will resolve the dispute.

